high_descs: Turn left and go across to the dining table.
Pick up the knife on the dining table.
Turn around to the bowl on the sofa.
Place the knife in the bowl on the sofa.
Pick up the bowl from the sofa.
Turn right and go straight across to the sink in the bathroom.
Place the bowl with the knife in it in the sink in the bathroom.
anns.task_desc: Place a bowl with a knife in it in the bathroom sink.

high_descs: Turn left and approach the wood dining table
Pick up the knife from the table
Turn right and walk up to the sofa
Put the knife down on the bowl
Pick up the bowl with knife from the sofa
Turn right and walk forward to the sink in the kitchen
Put the bowl with knife down in the bathroom sink
anns.task_desc: Put the bowl with knife in the bathroom sink

high_descs: Turn left to reach the dining table.
Pick up the knife from the dining table.
Turn right to reach the bowl on the sofa.
Put the knife on the bowl on the sofa.
Pick up the bowl from the sofa.
Turn right to reach the bathroom and turn left to reach the sink.
Put the bowl in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the bowl with the knife  in the sink.
